<configuration>
<property>
<name>yarn.nodemanager.aux-services</name>
<value>mapreduce_shuffle</value>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.nodemanager.aux-services.mapreduce.shuffle.class</name>
<value>org.apache.hadoop.mapred.ShuffleHandler</value>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.resourcemanager.scheduler.address</name>
<value>hadoop-mn01:8030</value>
<disciption>ResourceManager 对ApplicationMaster暴露的访问地址。</disciption>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.resourcemanager.resource-tracker.address</name>
<value>hadoop-mn01:8031</value>
<disciption> ResourceManager 对NodeManager暴露的地址。</disciption>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.resourcemanager.address</name>
<value>hadoop-mn01:8032</value>
<disciption>ResourceManager 对客户端暴露的地址。</disciption>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.resourcemanager.admin.address</name>
<value>hadoop-mn01:8033</value>
<disciption>ResourceManager 对管理员暴露的访问地址。</disciption>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.nodemanager.address</name>
<value>0.0.0.0:8034</value>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.nodemanager.webapp.address</name>
<value>0.0.0.0:8088</value>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.resourcemanager.webapp.address</name>
<value>hadoop-mn01:8089</value>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.nodemanager.local-dirs</name>
<value>/data/hadoop/nodemanager/tmp/</value>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.nodemanager.remote-app-log-dir</name>
<value>/data/hadoop/nodemanager/remote</value>
</property>
<property>	
<name>yarn.nodemanager.log-dirs</name>
<value>/data/hadoop/nodemanager/logs</value>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.nodemanager.log.retain-seconds</name>
<value>604800</value>
</property>                                                                          
<property>
<name>yarn.nodemanager.resource.cpu-vcores</name>
<value>10</value>
<disciption> NodeManager总的可用虚拟CPU个数。</disciption>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.nodemanager.resource.memory-mb</name>
<value>49152</value>
<disciption> NodeManager总的可用物理内存。</disciption>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.nodemanager.vmem-pmem-ratio</name>
<value>4</value>
<disciption> 每使用1MB物理内存，最多可用的虚拟内存数。</disciption>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.scheduler.minimum-allocation-mb</name>
<value>256</value>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.scheduler.maximum-allocation-mb</name>
<value>8192</value>
<disciption>container最小可申请的内存。在调度器中，很多资源计算部分会转化为这个最小值的N倍进行计算。所以，设定可分配内存等资源的时候，最好是刚好为这个最小值的倍数。</disciption>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.scheduler.minimum-allocation-vcores</name>
<value>1</value>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.scheduler.maximum-allocation-vcores</name>
<value>10</value>
</property>
<property>
<name>yarn.log-aggregation-enable</name>
<value>true</value>
</property>
</configuration>
